OL,3,CGuernsey politician and wife arrested
OL,4,Cover harassment complaint
OL,6,FGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister and
OL,7,Fhis wife have revealed they were
OL,8,Farrested following a complaint
OL,9,Falleging harassment.
OL,11,FThe pair were arrested on Wednesday 3
OL,12,FDecember - six days after the
OL,13,Fpolitician survived a vote to suspend
OL,14,Fhim from the States of Guernsey.
OL,16,FThe politician has confirmed that they
OL,17,Fhave been released under caution - but
OL,18,Fwithout charge - after being
OL,19,Finterviewed by Guernsey's police.
