OL,6,FIn a statement, Deputy St Pier said:
OL,7,F"My wife and I are the subjects of an
OL,8,Finvestigation following a complaint
OL,9,Falleging harassment.
OL,11,F"This is a shocking allegation which
OL,12,Fwe completely refute. We were arrested
OL,13,Fjust six days after my exoneration by
OL,14,Fthe States of Deliberation when the
OL,15,FAssembly voted overwhelmingly to
OL,16,Freject my proposed suspension in
OL,17,Frespect of an earlier complaint."
