OL,6,FIt follows an investigation that found
OL,7,Fhe broke the States' Code of Conduct
OL,8,Ffor talking to a Guardian reporter
OL,9,Fabout families' safeguarding
OL,10,Fcomplaints related to local Dr Sandie
OL,11,FBohin.
OL,13,F"We have stated unequivocally that we
OL,14,Fdeny any wrongdoing whatsoever. The
OL,15,F(police interviews) did not refer to
OL,16,Fany material information that is not
OL,17,Falready in the public domain," Deputy
OL,18,FSt Pier stated.
