OL,6,F"We naively imagined that we could
OL,7,Ffinally move on with our lives after
OL,8,Fnearly four years of complaints being
OL,9,Flodged against me.
OL,11,F"We are hopeful that this will be the
OL,12,Fend of the matter."
OL,14,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez,
OL,15,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, says that
OL,16,Fthe Policy & Resources Committee (P&R)
OL,17,Fare aware of the arrest.
