OL,6,FA statement from the P&R President
OL,7,Freads: "I am currently off-island,
OL,8,Frepresenting Guernsey at the British
OL,9,FIrish Council in Wales, so the other
OL,10,Fmembers of P&R and I have not yet had
OL,11,Fa chance to discuss this matter.
OL,13,F"We will consider it at the earliest
OL,14,Fopportunity and will provide an update
OL,15,Fonce we have done so. Please bear with
OL,16,Fus in the meantime."
