OL,6,FIn a statement, Guernsey Police said:
OL,7,F"On the morning of 3 December,
OL,8,FGuernsey Police arrested both a 58-
OL,9,Fyear-old man and a 58-year-old woman
OL,10,Fon suspicion of harassment.
OL,12,F"Enquiries are now ongoing, and no
OL,13,Ffurther comment will be provided while
OL,14,Fthe investigation continues."
